{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1350418_translations":{"at":1773688718890,"data":{"id":1350418,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yusuke Kobayashi is a Japanese voice actor. He is affiliated with Yu-rin Pro. In 2017, he won the Best New Actor Award at the 11th Seiyu Awards. He was born in Tokyo, and is 1.64 m tall.","name":"Yusuke Kobayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小林裕介（こばやし ゆうすけ，Kobayashi Yuusuke），1985年3月25日出生于日本东京都，日本的男性声优，所属事务所为YU-RIN PRO。\n\n代表作有《晨曦公主》守元（苏芳）、《魔女的使命》多华宫仄、《亚尔斯兰战记》亚尔斯兰、《没有黄段子的无聊世界》奥间狸吉、《彗星路西法》宗吾·天城、《Re：从零开始的异世界生活》菜月昴、《这个美术社大有问题！》内卷昴、《风夏》榛名优、《如果有妹妹就好了。》羽岛伊月、《高达创形者》三上陆、《贤者之孙》西恩·沃夫特、《Dr.STONE》石神千空、《炎炎消防队》亚瑟·波义耳、《超人高中生们即便在异世界也能从容生存！》御子神司等。","name":"小林裕介","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Yusuke Kobayashi es un actor de doblaje japonés de Tokio que está afiliado a Yu-rin Pro. En 2017, ganó el premio al mejor actor revelación en los 11.º Seiyu Awards. Mide 1,64 m.","name":"Yusuke Kobayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"코바야시 유스케","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小林裕介是日本的男性聲優。出身於東京都，畢業於 AMUSEMENT MEDIA 綜合學院聲優藝人科，所屬公司為 YU-RIN PRO。","name":"小林裕介","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"小林裕介","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yusuke Kobayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yusuke Kobayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","eng